			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"a2190347da0fc70b",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 二、二次型的标准型、规范型\n==***最基础最重要的内容！后续一切的起点!***==",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":6083,
			"y":6600,
			"width":500,
			"height":160,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{
			"id":"85c1487a8be9aa12",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"1. 定义、必要条件、常用性质；\n\t1. 重要的必要条件--杀手锏：若 $A$ ~ $B$，有 $r(λE-A)=r(λE-B)$ ==(在λ为重特征值时特别好用--易算)==\n2. 判断/证明两个矩阵相似--流程图",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center","shape":"document"},
			"x":5897,
			"y":2211,
			"width":480,
			"height":260,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{
			"id":"72eea97c5edafb22",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### ==三、矩阵的相似对角化(近高频考点！P76 理论多看)==",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":5897,
			"y":1701,
			"width":440,
			"height":200,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{
			"id":"ab97f1513884a6ac",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 类型一、利用矩阵相似的必要条件及性质解决问题\n例 3",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":6857,
			"y":2101,
			"width":540,
			"height":199
		},
		{
			"id":"61c61cedd46e4dee",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 类型三、利用矩阵相似对角化求矩阵高次幂（计算量非常大，可用来练手）",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":7157,
			"y":1901,
			"width":460,
			"height":140
		},
		{
			"id":"788b9fa702e3653e",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 四、矩阵相似\n1. 概念性质多，全是经典题；\n2. 重点关注抽象矩阵相似；",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":5897,
			"y":2071,
			"width":480,
			"height":140
		},
		{"id":"a377d6979c070820","type":"file","file":"1. Math/2. 强化阶段/1. 线性代数/知识点整理/1. 行列式与矩阵/attachment/1-8--结合32页笔记看-4.png","x":6720,"y":-3208,"width":400,"height":128},
		{"id":"94d2c2e55ab43d9b","type":"file","file":"1. Math/2. 强化阶段/1. 线性代数/知识点整理/1. 行列式与矩阵/attachment/1-8--结合32页笔记看-1.png","x":6300,"y":-3418,"width":399,"height":138},
		{"id":"0cb7183c4187603e","type":"file","file":"1. Math/2. 强化阶段/1. 线性代数/知识点整理/1. 行列式与矩阵/attachment/1-8--结合32页笔记看-2.png","x":6760,"y":-3441,"width":400,"height":201},
		{"id":"862010802af5d38c","type":"file","file":"1. Math/2. 强化阶段/1. 线性代数/知识点整理/1. 行列式与矩阵/attachment/1-8--结合32页笔记看-3.png","x":6260,"y":-3240,"width":400,"height":144},
		{
			"id":"34c6fc3472013cf9",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"##### 配方法\n1. 配方；\n2. 通过 $y=Px$ 反解 $x=Cy$，要的是矩阵 $C$！",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":7183,
			"y":6840,
			"width":537,
			"height":240
		},
		{
			"id":"0e3a3574092ff1dc",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 三、矩阵合同、惯性定理",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":6103,
			"y":7080,
			"width":360,
			"height":120
		},
		{
			"id":"02149b4a76c7a0ea",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"二次型与二次曲面--考前看一看，送分题。",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":6883,
			"y":7300,
			"width":400,
			"height":80
		},
		{
			"id":"dcf828d5ea032e34",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"惯性定理的灵活运用！特别是和矩阵的==特征值==，==秩==联系起来！",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":6980,
			"y":7160,
			"width":360,
			"height":80
		},
		{
			"id":"11e0d872807cbd20",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 矩阵",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":4040,
			"y":-4840,
			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"7b7ae591cbf8cabb",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**例 2--模式识别**\n给 $AB=A+B$ 必有 $AB=BA$",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":5780,
			"y":-4350,
			"width":300,
			"height":80
		},
		{
			"id":"bffc9e6df5243c74",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 四、矩阵的高次幂--五种类型\n1. 试算找规律；\n2. 幂 0 型矩阵；\n3. 二项展开型；\n4. 秩 1 矩阵；\n5. 相似对角型（少用，化对角繁琐）",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":5295,
			"y":-4080,
			"width":500,
			"height":240
		},
		{
			"id":"7f260fffeb693e9c",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 六、矩阵乘法的进阶认识--常看\n**$AB=0$ 的 3 种角度：**\n1. 秩：$r(A)+r(B) \\leqslant n$；\n2. 方程角度；\n3. 特征值特征向量角度：$b_1, b_2...$ 是对应于 0 特征值的特征向量；",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":5330,
			"y":-3489,
			"width":420,
			"height":280
		},
		{
			"id":"a17c512f3ac3966a",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 七、矩阵的秩--重难点！\n1. 矩阵秩的等价说法-- $\\forall$... $\\exists$...\n2. ==***矩阵秩的相关结论(极其重要!)***==",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":5330,
			"y":-3106,
			"width":370,
			"height":200,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{
			"id":"3ff278fcf91e9eb3",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**例 5--关于 $a_{ij} + A_{ij}=0$ 的三个结论**",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":5380,
			"y":-4740,
			"width":360,
			"height":120
		},
		{
			"id":"bf9e0f3355ab79e7",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 1. 反对称矩阵的 3 条结论\n1. 反 1：$a_{ii}=-a_{ii}$\n2. 反 2：奇数阶的反对称矩阵行列式=0；\n3. 反 3：对于反对称矩阵 $A$，有任意 $x$ ，使得 $x^{T}Ax=0$",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":5820,
			"y":-5370,
			"width":440,
			"height":260
		},
		{
			"id":"359385529acd2ece",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 2. 伴随矩阵公式总结 P 19",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":5820,
			"y":-5020,
			"width":310,
			"height":100
		},
		{
			"id":"ef060c108f15f1f7",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**例 2--角度 1**",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":5430,
			"y":-4980,
			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"256d0b3c16a08441",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"#### 二、代数余子式与伴随矩阵--一通百通\n**两个角度：**\n1. 构造新的行列式求解；\n2. 转化为伴随矩阵",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":4640,
			"y":-5050,
			"width":460,
			"height":260
		},
		{
			"id":"b332b33d5eea59cc",
			"type":"text",
